org.jivesoftware.smack.roster

Interface RosterLoadedListener


  • public interface RosterLoadedListener
    Roster loaded listeners are invoked once the Roster was successfully loaded.

    A common approach is to call Roster.getEntriesAndAddListener(RosterListener, RosterEntries) within onRosterLoaded(Roster), to initialize or update your UI components with the current roster state.
